Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.56,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,but you rock the sailor uniform, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:42.61,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Squee! We match, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:45.50,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... that applies to everyone \Nelse at our school, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.99,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,It does seem a bit big on you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.49,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't want a more fitting size?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:54.75,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is your hand-me-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:57.04,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
