Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:25.07,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, viewers. It's time once \Nagain for {\i1}Notsu Notsu Shopping{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:28.38,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,And here's our item for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:31.07,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\c&H1C13AA&\3c&H9EC6D2&}Koshi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.07,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Our antler-shaped name seal case!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:35.33,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. It's so popular right now. \NI've been dying to get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:41.13,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\c&H262831&\pos(423,285)}yen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:39.19,DefaultTop,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, it's 29,800 yen after tax...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:41.25,DefaultTop,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,But just for you viewers today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:45.71,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(149,1)\fs18\c&H262831&\pos(288.5,285)}yen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:45.71,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(149,1)\fs18\c&H262831&\pos(555,285)}yen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:45.71,DefaultTop,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,We've slashed the price by 90%, \Nand it's only 2,980 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:48.97,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, 2,980 yen? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:51.72,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2.5\c&H1E212D&\3c&HF5F7F7&\pos(320,251)}Free Shipping
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:51.72,DefaultTop,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Buy three, and you'll get free shipping!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.84,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Act now, and we'll throw \Nin this antler plushie,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:57.24,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,this antler beauty essence, \Nand this wood-carved antler!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.48,DefaultItalics,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:05.75,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Really? An antler-shaped name seal case?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:09.24,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(382,1)\c&H000000&\fay0.145\pos(316,80.57)}Student Council Office
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:09.24,Signs_BText,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(529,1)\fs22\bord1\pos(480,277)}Locally, a Huge Hit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:13.33,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,You seem really happy, Chiharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:14.58,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.75,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,An antler-shaped name seal case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:19.62,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,An antler-shaped name seal case?! \NThat's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:27.96,Default,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,I also got an antler plushie, antler beauty \Nessence, and this wood-carved antler.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:31.08,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That plushie is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.89,Default,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Kinu. You can have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.78,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:39.85,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm such a failure as a childhood friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:42.96,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Chiharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:43.65,Default,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:46.65,Default,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,You're always taking care of me, Kinu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:52.53,Signs_BText,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(529,1)\fs20\bord1\pos(600,277)}At This Rate, You Could Get Them to Buy Anything
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.53,DefaultItalicsTop,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,An antler-shaped name seal case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:54.91,DefaultItalics,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Are they actually popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.43,DefaultItalics,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. It's not like I'd ever use one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:00.41,DefaultItalics,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,But it's free shipping...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.87,DefaultItalics,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,It's 90% off...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:05.88,DefaultItalics,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,And it comes with a plushie, a wood carving, \Nand beauty essence...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.42,DefaultItalics,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,2,980 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.46,DefaultItalics,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually... a good deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.28,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:16.22,Signs_BText,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(529,1)\fs20\bord1\pos(598,56.5)}Powerful Enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:20.18,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey. A cat. How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:22.39,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,But deer are much cuter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:23.94,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:27.97,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Dang, that wind's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:30.09,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,But Bashame is much stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.25,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, who are you even competing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:35.74,Signs_BText,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(529,1)\fs22\bord1\pos(503,277)}Koshitan Is Studying
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:39.59,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, I made you some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:41.49,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:43.25,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(320,110)}5 minutes later
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.75,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, I brought you a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:47.50,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.75,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(320,110)}Another 5 minutes later
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:51.70,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, I brought you more tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:53.97,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(320,110)}And another 5 minutes later
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:54.86,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.15,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Could you leave me alone for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:09:00.60,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(155,1)\fs12\bord2\fnArial Black\c&H32282D&\3c&H3B77BB&\pos(427.5,84)}Deer Club\N{\fs8}Seeking New Club Members
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:00.60,Signs_BText,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(529,1)\fs22\bord1\pos(598,56.5)}Surprisingly Athletic
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.85,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Newbie! Greet your senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.24,Default,Nokotan and Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Notsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:12.36,Signs_BText,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(529,1)\fs22\bord1\pos(40,59)}DEER CLUB THE ROCK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:12.36,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start a band!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:14.99,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get inspired by \Nsome late-night anime?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:18.63,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, I brought us instruments!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:20.01,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2.5\c&H1E212D&\3c&HF5F7F7&\pos(110.5,250.5)}Shakuhachi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:24.50,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2.5\c&H1E212D&\3c&HF5F7F7&\pos(470,60)}Theremin
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:24.50,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2.5\c&H1E212D&\3c&HF5F7F7&\pos(562.5,109.5)}Udu drum
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:21.59,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,The hell is this lineup?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:24.50,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even imagine what kind of \Nmelody they'd produce together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.39,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll play the vuvuzela.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:28.67,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,You're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:31.38,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, what?! \NThat wasn't even in the lineup!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.69,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Bashame can whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:37.11,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,You're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:40.22,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really need someone \Nto whistle in a band?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:41.35,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,And she can't even whistle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.19,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll be the vocalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:44.14,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:49.00,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Koshitan... on udu drum, \Ntheremin, and shakuhachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:53.03,Signs_BText,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18\pos(18,76.5)}Shizuoka Prefecture\NMishima Taisha
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:56.53,Signs_BText,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18\pos(23,110)}Shizuoka Prefecture\NMishima Taisha\NSacred Deer Park
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:59.78,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally summertime in Hino City!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:05.62,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've thought summer would \Ncome to Hino City... Right, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:08.78,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, summer comes \Nto Hino City all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.44,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,You and the narrator guy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:14.27,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,seem to think Hino is some ominous place \Noutside the human realm and understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:17.30,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... the manga went for over \Nthree years without one summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:20.30,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway. Our summer \Nuniforms are nice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.50,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:24.61,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Even if our uniforms are old hat by now, \Njust shortening the sleeves
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:27.18,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,adds a refreshing bit of eye candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.06,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.31,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:35.02,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at how much of your upper arm \Nshows thanks to those short sleeves!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:39.32,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention the glimpses of your alluring \Narmpits that show through the hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.21,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,An all-you-can-eat buffet for the eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.24,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:44.21,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell are you looking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:45.95,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,And, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:49.33,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,The faint outline on your back visible \Nthrough the thin summer uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:51.33,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,The pure-white love bra strap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.46,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are creeping me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.82,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're being so bashful, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:55.99,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:58.61,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Don't inch closer to me \Nwith those predatory eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:01.13,Default,Classmate A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Koshi-san and her little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:03.82,Default,Classmate C,0000,0000,0000,,They're so close even when \Nit's bright and early.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:05.85,Default,Classmate B,0000,0000,0000,,Sister yuri... I can dig it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:08.23,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey. It's Koshitan and Koshian!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:10.02,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,And now more predators.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:13.01,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best at being deer as usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:15.40,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, what the hell happened to you now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.65,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12\bord2\fnArial Black\c&H32282D&\3c&H062C9B&\pos(428,82)}Deer Club\N{\fs8}Seeking New Club Members
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.65,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, a bunch happened, \Nand now it's after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:22.08,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, but I guess \Nit's not going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:24.03,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Does anything feel strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:26.66,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! My antlers are moving just fine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:29.22,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Antlers aren't supposed to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:31.92,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:36.67,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Did you eat something off the ground \Nand catch some weird disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:41.06,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,How rude! The only thing I eat \Noff the ground is deer crackers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:42.85,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,So you {\i1}are{\i0} eating things off the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:47.58,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,But it's rare to find deer crackers randomly \Nlying on the ground outside of Nara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:49.52,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Bashame has figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:52.65,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Bashame has seen those spots \Nthat are on your body before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:55.25,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,And it is indeed a disease!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:57.77,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, seriously, Bashame?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:01.15,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The disease Nokotan-senpai has is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.82,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:03.79,DefaultTop,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:05.37,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:07.05,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,The arch-nemesis of rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:09.87,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,It's rice blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:14.12,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Rice blast is a disease caused by a \Nfungus that can grow in rice paddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:18.38,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,White splotches appear on \Nthe leaves of infected plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:22.95,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,If the symptoms worsen, the plant \Nwill eventually wither completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:27.41,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Not only does it reduce the yield of the rice \Nharvest, it can even kill off entire paddies,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:30.81,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,making it the disease that rice farmers \Nare the most afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.77,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,That's not even an animal disease!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.63,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:38.00,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Bashame watches {\i1}THE TETSUWAN DASH{\i0} \Nall the time, so Bashame knows lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.52,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(484,1)\fnTimes New Roman\pos(180,16.5)\c&HF8F6ED&\shad1\4a&H33&}Shut your mouth, Koshitan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:42.51,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, DASH {\i1}is{\i0} a great show...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:43.95,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,But that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.32,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is really pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:49.47,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I guess I was a rice plant, \Nnot a deer, all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:54.34,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Shika-san and Ine-san are like \Nold names for women in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:58.93,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Bashame respects you as \Na deer, Nokotan-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:03.32,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,But... as someone who worries about \NJapan's food self-sufficiency rates declining,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:05.26,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,rice blast must be taken care of!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:09.76,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\fnArial Black\c&H734DEA&\bord1.5\3c&HECECEC&}M{\c&H335483&}y {\c&HD06F80&}D{\c&H335483&}eer {\c&H04BFF4&}F{\c&H335483&}riend {\c&H2BD8A8&}N{\c&H335483&}okotan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:09.76,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue to support the social \Nstudies anime {\i0}My Deer Friend Nokotan{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:12.90,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, Bashame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:19.31,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go causin' trouble for all the \Nrice farmers in Japan with my sickly body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.15,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Shikanoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:23.25,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Deer don't truly die. They just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:26.61,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Koshitan, I leave the Deer Club in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.61,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(443,1)\an9\fnTimes New Roman\fs24\c&H250A86&\3c&H58B4DE&\bord2\pos(613.5,180.5)}D{\3c&HF9FBFF&}e{\3c&H58B4DE&}e{\3c&HF9FBFF&}r {\3c&H58B4DE&}C{\3c&HF9FBFF&}r{\3c&H58B4DE&}a{\3c&HF9FBFF&}c{\3c&H58B4DE&}k{\3c&HF9FBFF&}e{\3c&H58B4DE&}r{\3c&HF9FBFF&}s
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.57,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:32.08,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,This whole club was your idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.62,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,See ya... Koshitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.64,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shikanoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:54.96,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Koshitan-senpai sure does get \Ninfluenced by the mood easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:58.18,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of the best \Nthings about my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.65,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fnTimes New Roman\fs26\c&H250A86&\3c&H58B4DE&\bord2\pos(619.5,69)}D{\3c&HF9FBFF&}e{\3c&H58B4DE&}e{\3c&HF9FBFF&}r {\3c&H58B4DE&}C{\3c&HF9FBFF&}r{\3c&H58B4DE&}a{\3c&HF9FBFF&}c{\3c&H58B4DE&}k{\3c&HF9FBFF&}e{\3c&H58B4DE&}r{\3c&HF9FBFF&}s
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:03.36,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Tsunoda-san, are you slacking off again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:05.90,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's hot, but you \Nshouldn't be doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.09,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happened to him being a "wild" deer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.38,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shikanoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:15.16,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Tsunoda-san's body...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:19.29,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnTimes New Roman\fs16\c&H250A86&\3c&H58B4DE&\bord2\pos(432.5,146)}D{\3c&HF9FBFF&}e{\3c&H58B4DE&}e{\3c&HF9FBFF&}r {\3c&H58B4DE&}C{\3c&HF9FBFF&}r{\3c&H58B4DE&}a{\3c&HF9FBFF&}c{\3c&H58B4DE&}k{\3c&HF9FBFF&}e{\3c&H58B4DE&}r{\3c&HF9FBFF&}s
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:17.08,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Notsu? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.29,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,We match, Tsunoda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:25.72,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, maybe she's not sick. \NMaybe she's just molting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:26.55,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Molting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:34.17,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Twice per year, deer molt in order to \Nchange into their summer or winter coats.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:37.84,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And the noticeable spots that \Nshow up on their summer coats
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:39.69,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,are also known as the "kanoko" design.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:43.57,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you've seen it on the back \Nof that one world-famous fawn—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:47.77,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! When it comes to copyright, that's \Nthe one company you don't want to mess with!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:51.15,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,That story's in the public domain now, \Nso should be fine... probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:54.93,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so I was just molting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:57.08,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Whoopsies. Tee-hee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:15:06.96,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\fnComic Sans MS\c&H151E2A&\pos(389,31)}April ~ May
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:15:01.37,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Note: deer actually change into their \Nsummer coats between April and May.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:05.38,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,But we're just some dumb comedy anime, \Nso don't think about it too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:06.96,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call us dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:10.76,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Bashame believed in you from \Nthe start, Nokotan-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:11.59,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:15.56,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no wonder I shed \Nso much since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:16.97,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:20.89,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's definitely \Nthe other kind of molting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:24.11,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,What? I mean this clearly all hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:26.37,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Look, that's terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:28.36,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! My fur!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:34.16,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:37.01,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,The ventilation is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:40.25,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now that we're all \Ndressed for the season,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:42.67,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,let the Deer Club's summer officially begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:43.79,Default,Nokotan and Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:47.25,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:52.30,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean... I'm pretty sure this \Nsummer's gonna be insane, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:57.31,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Now that they're appropriately dressed, the \NDeer Club's hot summer can begin in earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:01.13,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Chiharu, is that a new antler?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:04.01,Default,Tsbuame,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I bought it for 2,000 yen on Mercari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.31,Default,Tsbuame,0000,0000,0000,,What a bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:08.04,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And then that hot summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.32,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,ended with no particular issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:15.19,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Was there a reason our hot summer \Ndidn't even make it to the end credits?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:18.10,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Heya, Anko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:23.71,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fnTimes New Roman\fs20\c&H250A86&\3c&H58B4DE&\bord2\pos(618.5,116)}D{\3c&HF9FBFF&}e{\3c&H58B4DE&}e{\3c&HF9FBFF&}r {\3c&H58B4DE&}C{\3c&HF9FBFF&}r{\3c&H58B4DE&}a{\3c&HF9FBFF&}c{\3c&H58B4DE&}k{\3c&HF9FBFF&}e{\3c&H58B4DE&}r{\3c&HF9FBFF&}s
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:22.35,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,All my fur molted again, so here's \Na fresh coat just for you, Koshian!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.71,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. My hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:27.21,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a waste, Anko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:29.96,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,These are so comfy to wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:32.34,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going \Nto be wearing that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:34.67,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Shedding hair, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:50.11,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Koshitan decided to halt her train of thought \Nbefore it arrived at a terrifying station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:53.11,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,So, about our plan \Nto eradicate the Deer Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:56.24,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have you two report on your progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:17:02.37,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Progress? But Chiharu and I aren't \Nexactly planning to eradicate it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:06.75,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,What? But you said you'd assist me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:09.25,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say anything of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:12.94,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Also, why are we back \Nto winter uniforms?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:15.68,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even get to show \Noff my summer uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:19.26,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even remember having \Nany kind of summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:26.45,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry! It's probably because \Nmy upper arms are so flabby and ugly
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:29.27,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,and visible with short sleeves \Nthat our summer just ended!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:32.28,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Your lack of a summer vacation \Nis a feature, not a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.18,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,May I have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:36.91,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Do you have something to report?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:41.22,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.45,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(193,1)\fnComic Sans MS\bord2\c&H7F6CEF&\3c&H665BBE&}Hiiiisss
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:43.45,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Deer Club eradication meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.21,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do it with the Deer Club here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:48.17,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time to sweat the small stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:51.13,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Small? It's your club we're eradicating!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:53.55,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I guess I shouldn't bring that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:56.44,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I have made the discovery of the century.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:58.34,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Of the century?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:17:59.83,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:03.12,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:04.06,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:05.35,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,It's a tsuchinoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:06.73,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,It absolutely is not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:10.69,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What in the world is this mysterious orb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:13.70,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,It moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.56,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Are those {\i1}tentacles{\i0} growing from it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:18.14,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,And it's squirming around! Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:20.38,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,What a unique shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:22.83,Default,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,The mysteries of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.83,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... You two are rather calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.13,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:28.39,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I found it when I was digging up \Nholes in the schoolyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:32.44,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing? And wait, \Nthat thing was buried on school grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:33.46,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:36.21,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, isn't the \Ntsuchinoko that one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:40.62,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,That unidentified lifeform... \Nwith the, uh, indescribable form...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:43.07,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,But this also has an indescribable form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:45.60,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it does! I mean, you have a point, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:48.74,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know that \Ntsuchinoko even really exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:53.32,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, now it's shining!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:55.73,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,See? I told you! It's a tsuchinoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:19:00.08,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second. Are we even \Nimagining the same tsuchinoko here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:02.86,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,This is clearly much \Ncreepier than a tsuchinoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.87,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,That's absolutely not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:06.24,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you so sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:09.90,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you being rash by saying it's \Nnot one because you subjectively think
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.50,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,its form and ecology are wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:14.38,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, have you ever \Nseen a tsuchinoko before?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:18.23,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really say without a doubt \Nthat this isn't a tsuchinoko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:21.51,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Conversely, why do you want it \Nto be a tsuchinoko that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:28.39,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait. Tsuchinoko... \NShikanoko... Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:31.39,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,that I now have a "deer friend" of my own?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:32.65,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:35.90,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\fnArial Black\c&H734DEA&\bord1.5\3c&HECECEC&}M{\c&H203956&}y {\c&HD06F80&}D{\c&H203956&}irt {\c&H04BFF4&}F{\c&H203956&}riend {\c&H2BD8A8&}T{\c&H203956&}suchinoko
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:35.91,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Our new show, {\i0}My Dirt Friend \NTsuchinoko{\i1}, is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:38.69,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,But the more you look at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:42.73,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,The way it feels, with its smooth skin \Nand ceramic-like finish...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:44.03,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,It might actually be cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:48.41,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard anyone describe \Nan unidentified lifeform that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:49.71,Default,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,Tsucchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.19,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you named it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:54.04,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,You feel so fondly about it \Nthat you gave it a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:57.67,Default,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't seem as energetic as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:01.08,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Was it trying to say something to us \Nwhen it shone before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:03.66,Default,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:05.93,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Let's feed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:08.73,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Feed it? You don't even know what tsuchi—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:11.68,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,what that thing eats, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:14.67,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,It eats deer crackers, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.31,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "of course"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.82,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. I've got a yummy \Ndeer cracker for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:20.50,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:22.57,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1.5\fnComic Sans MS\c&HE3C4B2&\3c&HA57C71&}Harrumph
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:27.22,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't like deer crackers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:28.50,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about some grass?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:30.54,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe some boba?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:30.54,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\an7\fad(127,1)\bord1.5\fnComic Sans MS\c&HE3C4B2&\3c&HA57C71&}Harrumph
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:31.66,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Say it ain't so!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:34.81,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why don't you just try one bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:35.38,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.80,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Is that intimidation? \NIs it trying to intimidate you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:44.69,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait... Could it be that... \Nyou're not a tsuchinoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:47.55,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've been telling you \Nthis whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:53.18,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Neko-chan's retorts fill Koshitan's shoes so \Nseamlessly, you can hardly tell she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:56.25,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, after trying \Nto feed it various things...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:59.44,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to like chalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.91,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:05.02,Default,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,A photo of Tsucchi and \NNokotan-senpai together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:06.45,Default,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,Super rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:11.24,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how you all can give \Nthat unknown thing so much attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:13.94,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's basically the same as a dog \Nor a cat once you get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:16.08,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,You should try touching it, too, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:18.84,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,What...? Touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:21.66,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:36.39,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.48,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm la—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:44.27,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Wha, whoa... What the heck \Nis that mysterious organism?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:45.82,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,...ko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:47.57,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Nekoyamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.45,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,It's a tsuchinoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:52.49,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... No, it definitely is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:55.66,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, what's \NShikanoko-san doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:57.93,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,I will raise this little one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:21:59.46,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:04.50,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The Deer Club and student council decided \Nto take responsibility and raise it together.
